# Vercel only needs the static site (public/) and the serverless API (api/).
# Everything below is for pip/MCP distribution or local tooling — keep it OUT of the
# Vercel build so Vercel doesn't try to resolve/lock the Python package (the `mcp`
# extra requires Python >=3.10 and breaks Vercel's dependency resolver).
pyproject.toml
src/
mcp/
scripts/
data/
docs/
README.md
LICENSE
.gitignore
